  <brief_title>Motorized Continuous Cold Therapy Versus Standard Post-op Icing Protocol for Two Foot and Ankle Procedures</brief_title>
  <official_title>Motorized Continuous Cold Therapy Versus Standard Post-op Icing Protocol for Two Foot and Ankle Procedures: An Evaluation of Narcotic Consumption, Pain, Wound Healing, and Patient Satisfaction</official_title>
